207
00:13:51,741 --> 00:13:53,538
Mom, look...

208
00:13:53,581 --> 00:13:56,891
I know that I keep
messing everything up...

209
00:13:56,941 --> 00:14:01,457
and I know that I let you down.

210
00:14:03,261 --> 00:14:06,014
