515
00:34:15,231 --> 00:34:17,426
And the words
are just whispers and lies

516
00:34:17,471 --> 00:34:22,943
That I'll never believe

517
00:34:24,631 --> 00:34:29,068
And I want a moment to be real

518
00:34:29,111 --> 00:34:32,023
Want to touch things
I don't feel

519
00:34:32,071 --> 00:34:37,020
Want to hold on
and feel I belong

520
00:34:37,071 --> 00:34:41,462
How can you say I never change?

521
00:34:41,511 --> 00:34:44,264
They're the ones
that stay the same

522
00:34:44,311 --> 00:34:46,188
I'm the one now

523
00:34:46,231 --> 00:34:50,941
'Cause I'm still here

524
00:34:50,991 --> 00:34:55,860
