my praises when I left home.

534
00:35:44,431 --> 00:35:46,103
But I'm gonna change all that.

535
00:35:46,151 --> 00:35:49,143
Are you now? How so?

536
00:35:49,191 --> 00:35:52,581
I got some plans.

537
00:35:52,631 --> 00:35:55,668
Gonna make people see me
a little different.

538
00:35:58,631 --> 00:36:01,987
Sometimes, plans go astray.

539
00:36:02,031 --> 00:36:04,340
Not this time.

540
00:36:12,911 --> 00:36:15,744
Thank you, Morphy.

541
00:36:17,951 --> 00:36:21,182
So, how'd that happen anyway?

542
00:36:24,071 --> 00:36:29,191
You give up a few things
chasing a dream.

543
00:36:29,231 --> 00:36:31,267
Was it worth it?

544
00:36:36,951 --> 00:36:38,748
I'm hoping it is, Jimbo.

545
00:36:38,791 --> 00:36:41,259
I most surely am.

546
00:36:47,711 --> 00:36:49,702
What the devil?

547
00:36:49,751 --> 00:36:52,345
Good heavens.
The star Pelusa...

548
00:36:53,791 --> 00:36:55,668
