549
00:36:55,711 --> 00:36:57,781
Evasive action, Mr Turnbuckle!

550
00:36:57,831 --> 00:36:59,059
Aye-aye, Captain.

551
00:37:01,751 --> 00:37:05,300
All hands,
fasten your lifelines!

552
00:37:17,831 --> 00:37:21,141
Mr Arrow, secure those sails!

553
00:37:21,191 --> 00:37:23,466
Secure all sails!

554
