Silver!

557
00:37:51,071 --> 00:37:52,982
Thanks, lad.

558
00:38:13,711 --> 00:38:17,750
Captain, the star!

559
00:38:17,791 --> 00:38:20,259
It's devolving into a...

560
00:38:20,311 --> 00:38:23,701
