00:38:48,871 --> 00:38:51,749
We'll ride that last magilla
out of here.

570
00:38:51,791 --> 00:38:53,986
All sails secured, Captain!

571
00:38:54,031 --> 00:38:57,546
Good man!
Now release them immediately!

572
00:38:58,831 --> 00:39:01,470
Aye, Captain.
You heard her, men.

573
00:39:01,511 --> 00:39:03,581
Unfurl those sails.

574
00:39:03,631 --> 00:39:05,144
- What?
- But we just finished...

575
00:39:05,191 --> 00:39:08,547
- Tying them down!
- Make up your blooming minds!

576
00:39:10,391 --> 00:39:11,870
Mr Hawkins...

577
00:39:11,911 --> 00:39:15,665
make sure all lifelines
are secured good and tight!

578
00:39:15,711 --> 00:39:17,030
Aye-aye, Captain.

579
00:39:24,071 --> 00:39:27,143
