- Very good!

580
00:39:52,191 --> 00:39:54,989
Captain, the last wave!

581
00:39:55,031 --> 00:39:56,908
Here it comes!

582
00:39:56,951 --> 00:39:58,862
Hold on to your lifelines,
gents!

583
00:39:58,911 --> 00:40:01,266
It's gonna be a bumpy ride!

584
00:40:39,258 --> 00:40:42,011
Captain! Oh, my goodness.

585
00:40:42,058 --> 00:40:43,571
That was absolutely...
That was the most...

586
00:40:43,618 --> 00:40:45,893
Tish-tosh.
Actually, Doctor...

587
00:40:45,938 --> 00:40:48,657
your astronomical advice
was most helpful.

588
00:40:48,698 --> 00:40:52,168
Well, thank you.
Thank you very much.

589
00:40:52,218 --> 00:40:54,334
I have a lot of help
to offer anatomically...

590
00:40:54,378 --> 00:40:57,529
amanamonically...
as-astronomically.

591
00:40:57,578 --> 00:41:00,251
I must congratulate you,
Mr Silver.

592
00:41:00,298 --> 00:41:01,526
It seems your cabin boy...

593
00:41:01,578 --> 00:41:03,887
