Mr Arrow has been lost.

597
00:41:20,138 --> 00:41:22,971
His lifeline was not secured.

598
00:41:25,818 --> 00:41:27,297
No, I checked them all.

599
00:41:31,018 --> 00:41:34,408
I did. I checked them all.
They were secure.

600
00:41:34,458 --> 00:41:36,096
I swear.

601
00:41:46,698 --> 00:41:51,214
Mr Arrow was a...

602
00:41:51,258 --> 00:41:53,818
fine spacer...

603
00:41:53,858 --> 00:41:57,612
finer than most of us
could ever hope to be...

604
00:41:58,938 --> 00:42:01,975
but he knew the risks,
as do we all.

605
00:42:02,018 --> 00:42:05,454
Resume your posts.
We carry on.

606
00:42:29,178 --> 00:42:30,770
It weren't your fault,
you know?

607
00:42:33,658 --> 00:42:33,738
Half the crew would be spinning
in that black abyss...

608
00:42:33,738 --> 00:42:38,095
Half the crew would be spinning
in that black abyss...

609
00:42:38,138 --> 00:42:41,448
Don't you get it?
I screwed up!

610
00:42:41,498 --> 00:42:43,375
For two seconds,
I thought that maybe...

611
00:42:43,418 --> 00:42:46,649
I could do
something right, but...

612
00:42:46,698 --> 00:42:47,926
I just...

613
00:42:51,658 --> 00:42:54,536
Just forget it. Forget it.

614
00:43:00,538 --> 00:43:04,770
Now, you listen to me,
James Hawkins.

615
00:43:04,818 --> 00:43:08,015
You got the makings
of greatness in ya...

616
00:43:08,058 --> 00:43:11,289
but you gotta take the helm
and chart your own course.

617
00:43:11,338 --> 00:43:14,648
Stick to it,
no matter the squalls...

618
00:43:14,698 --> 00:43:16,814
and when the time comes
you get the chance...

619
00:43:16,858 --> 00:43:19,088
to really test
the cut of your sails...

620
00:43:19,138 --> 00:43:24,417
and show what you're made of,
I hope I'm there...

621
00:43:24,458 --> 00:43:28,929
catching some of the light
coming off ya that day.

622
00:43:40,498 --> 00:43:42,454
There, there.

623
00:43:42,498 --> 00:43:45,217
Lad, it's alright, Jimbo.

624
00:43:45,258 --> 00:43:47,772
It's alright.

625
00:43:51,018 --> 00:43:53,737
Now, Jim, I...

626
00:43:53,778 --> 00:43:56,133
I best be getting
about my watch...

627
00:43:56,178 --> 00:43:59,090
and you best be getting
some shut-eye.

628
00:44:14,338 --> 00:44:18,172
Getting in too deep here,
Morphy.

629
00:44:18,218 --> 00:44:22,291
Next thing ya know, they'll be
saying I've gone soft.

630
00:45:07,366 --> 00:45:10,119
Morph, knock it off.
It's too early for this.

631
00:45:16,286 --> 00:45:18,322
Come back here!

632
00:45:22,166 --> 00:45:23,394
Gotcha, Morph!

633
00:45:27,006 --> 00:45:28,997
That's it, you little squid.

634
00:45:49,446 --> 00:45:51,118
Busted!

635
00:45:53,406 --> 00:45:56,364
What we're saying is
we're sick of all this waiting.

636
00:45:56,406 --> 00:45:57,634
There's only
three of them left.

637
00:45:57,686 --> 00:45:59,802
We are wanting to move.

638
00:45:59,846 --> 00:46:02,599
We don't move till
we got the treasure in hand.

639
00:46:02,646 --> 00:46:05,843
I say we kill 'em all now.

640
00:46:05,886 --> 00:46:09,196
I say what's to say!

641
00:46:09,246 --> 00:46:10,964
Disobey my orders again...

642
00:46:11,006 --> 00:46:12,917
like that stunt you pulled
with Mr Arrow...

643
00:46:12,966 --> 00:46:15,766
and so help me,
you'll be joining him!

644
00:46:15,766 --> 00:46:16,403
and so help me,
you'll be joining him!

645
00:46:18,726 --> 00:46:23,846
Strong talk,
but I know otherwise.

646
00:46:23,886 --> 00:46:26,400
You got something to say,
Scroop?

647
00:46:26,446 --> 00:46:30,234
It's that boy.

648
00:46:30,286 --> 00:46:35,041
Methinks you have
a soft spot for him.

649
00:46:37,166 --> 00:46:40,124
Now, mark me, the lot of ya.

650
00:46:40,166 --> 00:46:43,636
I care about one thing,
and one thing only!

651
00:46:43,686 --> 00:46:46,200
Flint's trove.

652
00:46:46,246 --> 00:46:48,237
You think I'd risk it all
for the sake...

653
00:46:48,286 --> 00:46:51,642
