little whelp?

654
00:46:51,686 --> 00:46:53,244
What was it now?

655
00:46:53,286 --> 00:46:57,996
"You got the makings
of greatness in ya."

656
00:46:58,046 --> 00:46:59,525
Shut your yap!

657
00:46:59,566 --> 00:47:03,844
I cosied up to that kid
to keep him off our scent.

658
00:47:03,886 --> 00:47:06,081
But I ain't gone soft.

659
00:47:06,126 --> 00:47:08,037
Land ho!

660
00:47:14,326 --> 00:47:16,362
There it is!

661
00:47:16,406 --> 00:47:19,125
Feast eyes and click heels
if you got 'em.

662
00:47:27,006 --> 00:47:28,997
Where the devil's me glass?

