00:47:41,566 --> 00:47:45,320
Playing games, are we?

664
00:47:45,366 --> 00:47:49,325
Yeah.
Yeah, we're playing games.

665
00:47:49,366 --> 00:47:55,999
I see. Well, I was
never much good at games.

666
00:47:56,046 --> 00:47:59,436
Always hated to lose.

667
00:48:01,406 --> 00:48:02,805
Me, too!

668
00:48:07,606 --> 00:48:08,834
Right-o...

669
00:48:12,406 --> 00:48:15,318
Blast it all.

