00:48:19,566 --> 00:48:22,126
Change in plan, lads!

671
00:48:22,166 --> 00:48:24,236
We move now!

672
00:48:28,446 --> 00:48:31,358
Strike our colours, Mr Onus.

673
00:48:31,406 --> 00:48:33,874
With pleasure, Captain.

674
00:48:47,532 --> 00:48:50,092
Pirates on my ship?
I'll see they all hang.

675
00:48:50,132 --> 00:48:51,451
Doctor, familiar with these?

676
00:48:51,492 --> 00:48:53,847
I've seen... I've read...

677
00:48:55,052 --> 00:48:56,690
No, I'm not.

678
00:49:00,252 --> 00:49:03,210
Mr Hawkins!
Defend this with your life.

679
00:49:03,252 --> 00:49:04,651
Morph! Give me that!

680
00:49:07,772 --> 00:49:10,411
You're taking all day about it.

681
00:49:18,812 --> 00:49:20,325
Stop them!

682
00:49:30,292 --> 00:49:32,487
To the longboats, quickly!

683
00:49:53,172 --> 00:49:55,732
Chew on this,
you pus-filled boils!

684
00:50:02,012 --> 00:50:04,207
Did you actually aim for that?

685
00:50:04,252 --> 00:50:05,924
Actually, I did.

686
00:50:12,772 --> 00:50:14,490
Blast it.

687
00:50:15,812 --> 00:50:17,768
