Morph, come here.

692
00:50:28,892 --> 00:50:31,531
Come here, boy.
Come to your dad.

693
00:50:31,572 --> 00:50:33,164
Come here, boy.

694
00:50:33,212 --> 00:50:34,964
- Come on!
- Morph, here!

695
00:50:48,092 --> 00:50:49,411
Now!

696
00:51:01,052 --> 00:51:03,327
Parameters met.
Hydraulics engaged.

697
00:51:04,532 --> 00:51:06,887
That's it! Come to papa!

698
00:51:06,932 --> 00:51:10,288
Hold your fire!
We'll lose the map!

699
00:51:12,212 --> 00:51:14,043
Captain!
Laser ball at 12 o'clock!

700
00:51:43,012 --> 00:51:44,809
Oh, my goodness.

701
00:51:44,852 --> 00:51:47,844
That was more fun
than I ever want to have again.

702
00:51:47,892 --> 00:51:52,647
That's not one of
my gossamer landings.

703
00:51:52,692 --> 00:51:53,886
Captain!

704
00:51:56,652 --> 00:51:57,971
Don't fuss.

705
00:51:59,572 --> 00:52:01,085
Slight bruising.
That's all.

706
00:52:01,132 --> 00:52:03,248
Cup of tea,
and I'll be right as rain.

707
00:52:03,292 --> 00:52:06,284
Mr Hawkins...

708
00:52:06,332 --> 00:52:07,845
